00:00:33.260 --> 00:00:36.260
ju do te shihni dicka vertete, sinqerisht pak-a shume integron

00:00:36.260 --> 00:00:39.260
boten dy dimensionale qe ne jetojme rehat

00:00:39.260 --> 00:00:41.260
